                <p>while enroute to Singapore, Mr. Newton was instructed to proceed to Gokolana for
                    temp. duty as Vice Consul (Commu. de Recond. Council of Yokohama, dated May 8,
                    1935.)</p>
                <p>R. Allen Haden designated Secretary of U.S. Delegation to London Naval Conf.,
                    Nov. 20, 1935.</p>
                <p>R. Allen Haden detailed to Dept. of State, temporarily, Jan. 8, 1936.</p>
